{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h1.png?t=1730552236\" />Interact with bizarre mechanisms, think out of the box to gain your freedom, and discover historical unsolved mysteries</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/1.gif?t=1730552236\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h2.png?t=1730552236\" />You will experience a real-life adventure while playing this puzzle game! Lots of intriguing puzzles are waiting for you, ensuring an immersive experience that will keep you engaged for hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/level.png?t=1730552236\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h3.png?t=1730552236\" />Examine several mechanisms to unlock each box and gain your freedom</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/2.gif?t=1730552236\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h4.png?t=1730552236\" />For an unforgettable experience, immerse yourself in the adventure by playing the game with your headphones on!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h5.png?t=1730552236\" />Click the bulb button to get hints that will help you through the game, or get in touch with the developer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h6.png?t=1730552236\" />This is an extra challenge that will keep your brain busy for days. Open the letter inside the Enigmas Box and crack a new riddle every day. How far can you go?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/eb.gif?t=1730552236\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/h7.png?t=1730552236\" />Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2535640/extras/xslogo.png?t=1730552236\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>XSGames</strong> is a solo indie game developer from Italy. I self-published the first Mystery Box chapter on the app stores in 2021 and was amazed by the awesome success it had with mobile game players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Such results changed my life, so I hope you'll enjoy playing the Mystery Box escape room adventures as much as I love making them!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Engima","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2535640/52c678f4c6038320308537803bb1b70100b49c2c.jpg"},{"name":"The 5 Enigmas","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/ap